Package com.google.auto.value.extension.serializable.serializer.impl

Class ImmutableMapSerializerExtension

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.auto.value.extension.serializable.serializer.impl.ImmutableMapSerializerExtension
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SerializerExtension
    @AutoService(SerializerExtension.class)
public final class ImmutableMapSerializerExtension
extends Object
implements SerializerExtension
    A SerializerExtension that deserializes objects inside an ImmutableMap.

    Enables unserializable objects inside an ImmutableMap to be serializable.
